{
  "chapter": "116",
  "title": "西南夷列传",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "西南夷诸国风俗",
      "text": "<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">西南夷</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">君长</span>以十来数计，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夜郎</span>最大；其西边<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">靡莫</span>一类以十来数计，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">滇</span>最大；自<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">滇</span>以北的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">君长</span>以十来数计，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">邛都</span>最大：这些都是梳椎髻发型，耕种田地，有城邑聚居。在其外围，西自<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">同师</span>以东，北至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">楪榆</span>，名为<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">巂</span>、<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">昆明</span>，都编发，随畜牧迁徙，没有固定居所，没有<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">君长</span>，方圆可达<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数千里</span>。从<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">巂</span>向东北，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">君长</span>以十来数计，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">徙</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">筰都</span>最大；自<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">筰</span>向东北，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">君长</span>以十来数计，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">厓駹</span>最大。他们的习俗或定居一处，或迁徙流动，都在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>的西边。自<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">厓駹</span>向东北，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">君长</span>以十来数计，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">白马</span>最大，都是<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">氐</span>人一类。这些都是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">巴蜀</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西南</span>之外的<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">蛮夷</span>。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "当初<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚威王</span>的时候，派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">将军</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄蹻</span>率兵沿<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长江</span>而上，攻略<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">巴</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黔中</span>以西地区。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄蹻</span>是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">楚庄王</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">苗裔</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：庄蹻\">蹻（庄蹻）</span>到了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">滇池</span>，方圆<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三百里</span>，附近是平地，肥沃富饶绵延<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数千里</span>，就以武力威慑使其归属<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。想要回去报告，正遇<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>夺了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">巴</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黔中</span>郡，道路阻塞不通，因而返回，就以他的部众在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">滇</span>称王，改变服饰，顺从当地习俗，统领那里。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝时<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">常頞</span>攻略修通了<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">五尺道</span>，这些国家大多设置了官吏。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十多年（时长）</span>后，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span>朝灭亡。到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝兴起，全部弃置这些国家而开启<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>地旧边关。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">巴蜀</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众有的私自出关经商，获取当地的<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">筰马</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">僰僮</span>、<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">髦牛</span>，因此<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">巴蜀</span>富庶。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "唐蒙通夜郎",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">建元六年</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">大行</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王恢</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">东越</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">东越</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了王<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：东越王郢\">郢（东越王郢）</span>来报。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：王恢\">恢（王恢）</span>凭借兵威派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">番阳令</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">唐蒙</span>前去晓谕<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>，以示其意。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>用<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">蜀枸酱</span>款待<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：唐蒙\">蒙（唐蒙）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：唐蒙\">蒙（唐蒙）</span>询问来源，对方说：\"路经<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西北</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">牂柯</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">牂柯江</span>宽数里，流到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">番禺</span>城下。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：唐蒙\">蒙（唐蒙）</span>回到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长安</span>，询问<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>的商人，商人说：\"只有<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>出产<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">枸酱</span>，很多人私自带出去卖到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夜郎</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夜郎</span>临近<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">牂柯江</span>，江宽<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百馀步</span>，足以行船。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>用财物役使归属<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夜郎</span>，西至<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">同师</span>，但也不能以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>子之礼役使他们。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：唐蒙\">蒙（唐蒙）</span>于是上书劝说皇上说：\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">南越王</span>乘<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">黄屋</span>车、插<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">左纛</span>旗，地域东西<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万馀里</span>，名义上是外<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>，实际上是一州之主。如今从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长沙</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">豫章</span>前往，水路多有中断，难以通行。我私下听说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夜郎</span>所拥有的精兵，可以得到<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀万</span>，乘船沿<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">牂柯江</span>而下，出其不意，这是制服越人的一条奇计。凭借<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝的强大、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">巴蜀</span>的富饶，开通<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夜郎</span>之道，为他们设置官吏，非常容易。\" <span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上</span>答应了。于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">拜</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：唐蒙\">蒙（唐蒙）</span>为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎中将</span>，率领<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">千人</span>，辎重粮草<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">万馀人</span>，从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">巴蜀</span><span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">筰关</span>进入，于是会见了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">夜郎侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">多同</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：唐蒙\">蒙（唐蒙）</span>厚加赏赐，用威德晓谕他，相约为之设置官吏，让他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">子</span>担任县令。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夜郎</span>附近的小城邑都贪图汉朝的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">缯帛</span>，认为<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>道险阻，最终不能占有此地，于是姑且听从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：唐蒙\">蒙（唐蒙）</span>的约定。回朝报告后，就把那里设为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">犍为</span>郡。征发<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">巴蜀</span>士卒开治道路，从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">僰道</span>直通<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">牂柯江</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>人<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">司马相如</span>也说<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">西夷</span>的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">邛</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">筰</span>可以设郡。派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：司马相如\">相如（司马相如）</span>以<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">郎中将</span>身份前去晓谕，都像<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">南夷</span>那样处置，设置一名<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">都尉</span>，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀县</span>，归属<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>郡。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "当时，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">巴蜀</span>四郡疏通开往<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">西南夷</span>之路，戍卒转运粮饷。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">数年（时长）</span>过去，道路不通，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">士</span>卒疲困、饥饿、离开潮湿之地病死者很多；<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">西南夷</span>又屡次反叛，调兵前去<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>讨，耗费钱财却无功。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上</span>为此忧虑，派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">公孙弘</span>前去视察。回来答复，说此事不妥。等到<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙弘\">弘（公孙弘）</span>任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">御史大夫</span>时，正在修筑<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">朔方</span>来依河逐<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">胡</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：公孙弘\">弘（公孙弘）</span>借机多次进言<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">西南夷</span>之害，可以暂且罢置，专力对付<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上</span>罢置了<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">西夷</span>，只留下<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">南夷</span>的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夜郎</span>两县一<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">都尉</span>，让<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">犍为</span>郡自己渐渐保守发展。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "张骞求身毒道",
      "text": "到<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元狩元年</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">博望侯</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">张骞</span>出使<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">大夏</span>回来，说他在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">大夏</span>时看见<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">蜀布</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">邛竹</span>、<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">杖</span>，派人询问来源，对方说：\"从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东南</span>的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">身毒国</span>运来，距离<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数千里</span>，是从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>的商人处买到的。\"或听说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">邛</span>西<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二千里</span>有<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">身毒国</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：张骞\">骞（张骞）</span>因而极力陈说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">大夏</span>在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>的西南方，仰慕<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>，忧虑<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">匈奴</span>阻隔其道，如果真能打通<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">蜀</span>地，则<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">身毒国</span>之路便近，有利无害。于是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>令<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王然于</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">柏始昌</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">吕越人</span>等人，从<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">西夷</span>以西秘密出使，去寻找<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">身毒国</span>。到了<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">滇</span>，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">滇王</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尝羌</span>把他们留住，为他们寻找西去的道路<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十馀辈</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">一年多（时长）</span>过去，都被<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">昆明</span>阻塞，没能通<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">身毒国</span>。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">滇王</span>与<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>使者交谈说：\"<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>和我比哪个大？\" <span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">夜郎侯</span>也是这样。因为道路不通的缘故，各自以为自己是一州之主，不知道<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>的广大。使者回来后，极力陈说<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">滇</span>是大国，值得大力结交亲附。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>由此留意。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "南越反与夜郎入朝",
      "text": "到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>反叛时，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上</span>派<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">驰义侯</span>借<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">犍为</span>之力征发<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">南夷</span>兵。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">且兰君</span>害怕远行，旁边的国家会俘掠他的老弱，就与他的部众反叛，<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了使者和<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">犍为太守</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>于是调发<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">巴蜀</span>曾<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span>过<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>的罪人和八名<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">校尉</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>之。恰逢<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>已<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>的八名<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">校尉</span>没有南下，就引兵返回，途中<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">头兰</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">头兰</span>，是常常阻隔<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">滇</span>道的那个。平定<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">头兰</span>后，就平定了<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">南夷</span>，设为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">牂柯</span>郡。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">夜郎侯</span>起初倚仗<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>灭亡之后，正逢汉军返回<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀反叛者，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夜郎</span>于是入朝。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上</span>封他为<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">夜郎王</span>。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">南越</span>被<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span>之后，等<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：且兰君\">且兰（且兰君）</span>、<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">邛君</span>，并<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>了<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">筰侯</span>，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">厓駹</span>都震恐，请求归<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">臣</span>并设置官吏。于是把<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">邛都</span>设为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">越巂</span>郡，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">筰都</span>设为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沈犁</span>郡，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">厓駹</span>设为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汶山</span>郡，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">广汉</span>西的<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">白马</span>设为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">武都</span>郡。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "滇王降汉置郡",
      "text": "<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">上</span>派<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">王然于</span>用<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">破</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">越</span>、<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">南夷</span>的兵威晓谕<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">滇王</span>入朝。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">滇王</span>的部众有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">数万人</span>，他东北方的<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">劳洸</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">靡莫</span>，都是同姓相互依附，不肯听命。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">劳洸</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">靡莫</span>数次侵犯汉使者和吏卒。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">元封二年</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>调发<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">巴蜀</span>兵<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">击</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span><span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">劳洸</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">靡莫</span>，率兵临近<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">滇</span>。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">滇王</span>当初就很友善，因此不<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀。<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">滇王</span>离开<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">西南夷</span>的纷乱，举国投降，请求设置官吏入朝。于是设为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">益州</span>郡，赐<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">滇王</span>以<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">王印</span>，仍然让他统领他的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">民</span>众。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "本段",
      "text": "<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">西南夷</span>的<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">君长</span>数以百计，只有<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夜郎</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">滇</span>受赐<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">王印</span>。<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">滇</span>是小邑，却最受宠。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "太史公论赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>国的祖先难道有天赐的福禄吗？在<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>代曾做<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名·规范：周文王\">文王（周文王）</span>的老师，封于<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>。 到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>朝衰微时，土地号称有<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五千里</span>。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">秦</span><span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>诸侯，唯独<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">楚</span>的<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">苗裔</span>还有<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">滇王</span>。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span><span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">西南夷</span>，很多国家被<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>，唯有<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">滇</span>再度成为受宠的王。 然而<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">南夷</span>事情的开端，起于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">番禺</span>见到<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">枸酱</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">大夏</span>见到<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">杖</span>和<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">邛竹</span>。 <span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">西夷</span>之后被剪灭，剽分为两方，最终设为七郡。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "西南外徼，由<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">庄蹻</span>首先开通。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">汉</span>朝因<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">大夏</span>之故，便命<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">唐蒙</span>前去。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">劳洸</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">靡莫</span>，风俗各异。 <span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夜郎</span>最大，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">邛</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">筰</span>称雄。 等到设置郡县，万代推其功。"
    }
  }
}